Grate @cucumber{0.5} and season with some @salt. Let stand for ~{5%min}. Squeeze the liquid out by hand. 
Add @Greek yogurt{200%g} and minced @garlic{2%cloves}.
Add @olive oil{2%tablespoons}, @lemon juice{1%tablespoon}, and a pinch of ground @black pepper{}.
Stir thoroughly.

Refrigerate for ~{30%min} before serving.
